title: Compiler fails to compile to macOS x86_64/arm64 on Linux

labels.name: A-linkage
labels.description: Area: linking into static, shared libraries and binaries

labels.name: T-compiler
labels.description: Relevant to the compiler team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue.

body:

From now on, it's unnecessary. drop(f); // Make 'file' immutable (There HAS to be a better way of doing this!) let file = file; println!("{}", file); todo!("Do something with file") } ``` ### Meta
